script = ExtResource("3_ver3l")
category = 1
text = "Vector Barbossa is the tall man in his 50s who is currently the Saint Joloise of Sugori. He is known for being quite charismatic and for his 2 pets, George and Jack the two monkeys. Vector has been a pirate for decades and is the captain of the Monkey Pirates despite his job not requiring a pirate crew. Many call him the \"Father of Justice\" and he is by far the most respected government official.

Firstly, back in his early days, Vector had a rough childhood. Vector Barbossa at the young age of 7, had his home town invaded by outsiders. His whole town got ransacked, pillaged, and his family was murdered in the process, along with much of the area. Vector got raised by his Aunt in a neighbouring island, he since then wanted to not only seek vengeance on the raiders but to prevent any other children from experiencing the trauma he has. Vector's favourite drink is whiskey as that is what his parents drank the night before the invasion for their anniversary, and also the last interaction he had with them.

Vector was a depressed child until he was mature enough to start trying to become a pirate. When he was 14, his uncle let him train by himself on \"Monkey Island\", where he learnt to fight and befriended many of the monkeys and apes that lived there. Then Vector trained for more years, before starting his own pirate crew, while he was also helping rebuild his hometown. He was doing this so that he could become a Joloise Lord and protect it. At the age of 18, he finally got to be a Joloise Lord. After a few years, Vector gets spotted by the then current Saint Joloise, Ricky Migrose. Migrose ends up noticing how big of a symbol of Sugori greatness Vector is, and ends up mentoring him almost like a son. A decade passes and Migrose retires, which leaves the Saint Joloise open, but the previous King Lord, Oscar \"Mantis\" Patrogas gained the spot and even chose Vector as his replacement. As Patrogas was on the older side and because he contracted a genetic disease, he retired early, and at the age of 38, Vector Barbossa became Saint Joloise where he put Ardina \"Steel Wrist\" Lockhart and Nidon the Restless as his 2 Kings. He has previously stated that getting that title means a lot to him. Around this time, his uncle passed away and gave control of the tourist business of Monkey Island to Vector, in which he used this to adopt George and Jack from the monkeys he befriended.

The Saint Joloise role is more like a governing job, yet Vector still enjoys a fight. Vector uses two pistols and also his impressive kicks to fight opposition in close quarters combat, but rarely shows any naval warfare in his missions. Even though he is their \"supervisor\", he rarely stops or commands his two Kings and believes people should protect with no command. This is backed up by the fact that it is known that Vector does not always listen to commands from his government equals but no one bats an eye, as they know it is all for the benefit of the people.

Vector has been a huge imporance in the overall events over the many years he's been a pirate, he was a key figure in the rescue of Gorgana Wretchirl, temporarily got placed as a Commander of the Army during the \"War with the 3 Nations\" and also the leader of the philanthropical movement of the \"Nice Pirate\" where pirates donated a large sum of their findings to poor areas of the Sugori Ilses. The Monkey Pirates are not that serious of a crew but have been very loyal since its beginning. It is mostly comprised of crew members who joined Vector at the beginning, a few names like Harrison Ford, Rorey J Martin, Elicia Ranford and son of a former Gira, Nancy \"Ship\" Rocks. Vector also has ex-Scareye pirate, Sanson the Vile on his team, as he is a valuable asset and was given to Vector Barbossa to contain him. The Monkey Pirates once had a temporary aliance with the Scareye Pirates nearly fourty years ago. It was in Vectors favour so that he could protect the city of Wotopolis, Vector always felt suspicious of Scareye, even then."
id = 65
name = "Vector Barbossa"
